<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/8(Sat.)Why you not really need 8 glasses of water per day/metals shortage make the climate crisis worse(Cecillia)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=496&amp;p=518#p518"><![CDATA[
5/8(Sat.)Why you might not really need 8 glasses of water per day/A shortage of these metals could make the climate crisis worse(Host:Cecillia)<br /><br />Article 1<br />Why you might not really need 8 glasses of water per day<br /><br /><a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2021/05/05/health/glasses-of-water-per-day-wellness-partner/index.html" class="postlink">https://edition.cnn.com/2021/05/05/health/glasses-of-water-per-day-wellness-partner/index.html</a><br /><br />1.How much water do you drink every day?and why do you think that's the appropriate amount for your body?<br />2.What do you think about the article? Would it change your habit of drinking water?<br />3.Please provide some sample of information that affect your drinking habit.<br /><br />Article 2<br />A shortage of these metals could make the climate crisis worse<br /><br /><a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2021/05/05/business/climate-crisis-metals-shortage/index.html" class="postlink">https://edition.cnn.com/2021/05/05/business/climate-crisis-metals-shortage/index.html</a><br /><br />1.What kind of metals are needed to produce clean energy mentioned in this article?<br />2.What could cause the price volatility of these rare metals?<br />3.Please share anything that could mes to your mind after reading the article.<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">///////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~</span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Fri May 07, 2021 10:57 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
